				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I think this is our first non-fantastic romantic piece. Also, are you the only person other than Parfles to attempt something romantic? I can&#8217;t remember. There definitely is something romantic about someone thinking so much about the meaning of the engagement ring.</p>
<p>The description of the gold and silver, the wearing of the ring and aging of the person, are great. As Docinatrix says, it does feel very meditative and thoughtful, and holds everything together.</p>
